Write the onboarding screens.

---

1. Welcome to SimpleHealth. We help you take your
   medication on time, every time. No fuss.

2. Tell us what you take and when. We'll send you
   a gentle nudge when it's time.

3. That's it. Tap the big green button to start.

>>:claude:assumed: screens have a Next button at the bottom
>>:claude:suggestion: say "press" instead of "tap" for elderly users
>>:claude:ref: Apple HIG Accessibility Guidelines 2026

